title: TMGW #61: Mamrie Cries in a Bar in Japan
description: Grace and Mamrie reconnect after almost a month apart. They discuss Mamrie’s trip to Japan and Bali, Grace’s trip back to the East Coast, Cats, Bars and Monkeys. It gets weird.
